name: Moroccan Flag

## Moroccan Flag

A limited edition flag to fly proudly on your farm

You can craft this item at the Goblin Tailor in the game.

## Supply

1000

### Crafting Costs

---

- 10 Wood
- 50 SFL

[Link](https://docs.sunflower-land.com/player-guides/rare-and-limited-items#flags)
